WEBVTT

00:01.542 --> 00:02.753
PREVIOUSLY ON "REVENGE"...

00:02.753 --> 00:04.215
EMILY: [ Distorted ]
I have your daughter.

00:04.215 --> 00:06.087
YOU ABDUCTED CHARLOTTE
TO GET THE GRAYSONS TO CONFESS?

00:06.087 --> 00:07.758
PUT ON THE BLINDFOLD --
I'M LETTING YOU GO.

00:07.758 --> 00:09.260
Charlotte: IF YOU DON'T HAVE
THE GUTS

00:09.260 --> 00:11.222
TO ADMIT WHAT YOU DID
TO MY REAL FATHER,

00:11.222 --> 00:12.473
I'LL TELL THE POLICE.

00:12.473 --> 00:16.597
I HAVE THE POWER
TO TAKE YOU OUT ANYTIME I WANT!!

00:16.597 --> 00:18.349
I WAS IN LEAGUE
WITH THE TERRORISTS

00:18.349 --> 00:22.022
WHO TRIED TO BRING ME DOWN,
BUT I'M STILL HERE.

00:22.022 --> 00:24.195
DAVID CLARKE
WAS MY PATSY!

00:24.195 --> 00:25.406
TURN ON THE TV
IN GRAYSON MANOR.

00:25.406 --> 00:27.858
THE TRANSMISSION YOU JUST SAW
 WAS LIVE

00:27.858 --> 00:30.030
FROM INSIDE
 THE GRAYSON HOUSE.

00:30.030 --> 00:31.242
WHAT ABOUT VICTORIA?

00:31.242 --> 00:32.283
OH,
I'M NOT FINISHED YET.

00:32.283 --> 00:33.744
IT WAS PROBABLY NOLAN.

00:33.744 --> 00:35.156
HE'S THE ONLY PERSON THAT'S
SMART ENOUGH TO PULL THIS OFF.

00:35.156 --> 00:36.327
WE OWN THE PROGRAM NOW.

00:36.327 --> 00:37.998
WE DON'T NEED YOU
TO MAKE IT A SUCCESS.

00:37.998 --> 00:39.500
YOU'RE OUT.

00:39.500 --> 00:41.122
Victoria: TAKE CHARLOTTE'S HAIR
AND CARL'S BLOOD TO THE LAB.

00:41.122 --> 00:43.084
HURRY, PLEASE.
A LIFE DEPENDS ON IT.

00:43.424 --> 00:44.835
I NEED ANSWERS.

00:44.835 --> 00:46.717
EVEN IF IT THREATENS
THE LAST MEMORY OF YOUR FATHER?

00:46.717 --> 00:49.260
CHARLOTTE RECEIVED LETTERS
FROM SOMEBODY PRETENDING
TO BE DAVID CLARKE.

00:49.260 --> 00:51.342
SHE AND I TRACKED HIM
TO HIS HOUSE -- THERE
WAS NO ONE THERE,

00:51.342 --> 00:53.053
BUT DIDN'T YOUR FATHER HAVE
SOMETHING LIKE THIS?

00:53.053 --> 00:55.055
THIS WAS MY FATHER'S.

00:56.137 --> 00:57.228
[ WIND WHISTLING ]

00:57.228 --> 00:58.559
Emily:
SORRY, DAD.

00:58.559 --> 01:00.681
WE WERE JUST
PLAYING TREASURE HUNT.

01:00.681 --> 01:02.103
David:
WELL [SIGHS]

01:02.103 --> 01:04.685
I'M GLAD THAT YOU AND JACK
TOOK THE TIME TO FIND IT.

01:04.685 --> 01:06.026
IT'S AN IMPORTANT RING.

01:07.108 --> 01:08.279
WHY?

01:08.279 --> 01:10.241
MY FATHER GAVE IT TO ME
WHEN I TURNED 18.

01:10.241 --> 01:13.033
SAID THAT I SHOULD RESPECT
THE FACT

01:13.033 --> 01:14.995
THAT A NAME MEANS A LOT
IN THIS WORLD.

01:14.995 --> 01:16.957
THAT'S WHY
MY INITIALS ARE ON IT.

01:16.957 --> 01:18.829
I WISH
I WOULD HAVE MET HIM.

01:18.829 --> 01:20.411
HE WAS A LOT LIKE YOU.

01:20.411 --> 01:23.164
HATED TO BE
COOPED UP INSIDE.

01:23.164 --> 01:25.166
BUT INSTEAD OF THE BEACH,
HE LOVED THE WOODS.

01:25.166 --> 01:26.837
SO MUCH SO
THAT HE EVEN BUILT A CABIN.

01:26.837 --> 01:30.090
WE WOULD GO
AND SPEND OUR SUMMERS THERE.

01:30.090 --> 01:31.552
YOU KNOW WHAT?

01:31.552 --> 01:33.714
I THINK I'M GONNA CONTINUE
THE FAMILY TRADITION

01:33.714 --> 01:35.266
WHEN YOU TURN 18.

01:35.266 --> 01:36.977
I'M GONNA GIVE YOU
SOMETHING.

01:47.278 --> 01:49.820
Aiden: YOU STILL THINKING
ABOUT THAT RING?

01:49.820 --> 01:53.033
YOU KNOW, MY FATHER ACTUALLY
MENTIONED A CABIN ONCE.

01:53.033 --> 01:54.995
YOU DON'T THINK
IT'S THE SAME PLACE

01:54.995 --> 01:57.037
WHERE JACK FOUND THIS,
DO YOU?

01:57.037 --> 01:59.079
THERE'S NOTHING TO BE GAINED
FROM INDULGING IN THAT HOPE.

01:59.079 --> 02:00.451
[ SIGHS ]

02:00.451 --> 02:03.083
ESPECIALLY WHEN REALITY'S
PRETTY DAMN GOOD RIGHT NOW.

02:04.084 --> 02:06.086
[ RING CLINKS ]

02:06.086 --> 02:08.589
[ CHUCKLES SOFTLY ]

02:08.589 --> 02:12.092
I WISH MY FATHER WAS HERE
TO SEE THIS.

02:12.092 --> 02:14.134
YEAH, MINE, TOO.
THEY'D BE PROUD OF US, AMANDA.

02:14.134 --> 02:16.016
WE'VE BEEN TO HELL AND BACK
FOR THEM.

02:16.016 --> 02:18.138
AND FOR EACH OTHER.

02:18.138 --> 02:20.221
I NEVER BELIEVED I'D FIND
A PARTNER IN THIS,

02:20.221 --> 02:22.183
NOR DID I EVER THINK
THAT WE'D FIND PEACE.

02:22.183 --> 02:24.525
OH, YE OF LITTLE FAITH.

02:24.525 --> 02:25.896
REALLY?
YOU'RE GONNA MAKE OUT

02:25.896 --> 02:27.268
LIKE THIS HAS ALL GONE
ACCORDING TO PLAN, ARE YOU?

02:27.268 --> 02:28.689
[ CHUCKLES ]

02:28.689 --> 02:32.072
NO, BUT I'M GONNA SAVOR THE HELL
OUT OF OUR VICTORIES.

02:33.153 --> 02:34.074
[ SIGHS ]

02:35.866 --> 02:37.828
I LOVE YOU, AIDEN.

02:49.750 --> 02:51.592
[ DOORS CREAKING, RATTLING ]

02:58.299 --> 03:01.101
Victoria: SINCE YOUR FATHER
AND I WERE TO BE MARRIED,

03:01.101 --> 03:02.603
I CONSIDER YOU FAMILY NOW.

03:02.603 --> 03:04.895
WE'LL HELP EACH OTHER
THROUGH THIS.

03:04.895 --> 03:08.269
OF COURSE, VICTORIA.
THANK YOU.

03:14.865 --> 03:17.077
I CAN'T KEEP UP THIS CHARADE
A MOMENT LONGER.

03:17.077 --> 03:20.451
MAYBE I SHOULDN'T HAVE TOLD YOU
THE TRUTH ABOUT YOUR FATHER.

03:20.451 --> 03:22.823
NO, YOU DID THE RIGHT THING,
DANIEL.

03:22.823 --> 03:24.084
IF I'M TO BE STRONG,

03:24.084 --> 03:26.627
I NEED TO KNOW
WHAT COULD HURT ME.

03:26.627 --> 03:29.460
ESPECIALLY
ABOUT THOSE CLOSEST TO ME.

03:46.477 --> 03:49.350
I STILL CAN'T BELIEVE
HE'S GONE.

03:49.350 --> 03:52.523
WELL, AT LEAST DAD'S
GONNA PAY.

03:52.523 --> 03:54.315
PROMISE TO TELL ME
WHAT IT'S LIKE

03:54.315 --> 03:57.197
WATCHING HIM SQUIRM IN
THE COURTHOUSE THIS AFTERNOON.

03:57.197 --> 03:58.449
ARE YOU KIDDING?

03:58.449 --> 04:01.452
MY PRESENCE WOULD BE
MISCONSTRUED AS SUPPORT.

04:01.452 --> 04:04.455
YOU'RE RIGHT.

04:04.455 --> 04:07.958
HE MUST BE LEFT ALONE...

04:07.958 --> 04:09.370
AND ABANDONED.

04:09.370 --> 04:12.633
AND WE CAN FINALLY PUT HIM
AND FLIGHT 197 BEHIND US.

04:12.633 --> 04:17.007
NOT UNTIL EMILY THORNE ALSO
FEELS THE PAIN OF THIS MOMENT.

04:38.699 --> 04:40.451
Judge Rivers:
SAVE IT FOR TRIAL.

04:40.451 --> 04:42.323
THIS IS MR. GRAYSON'S
BAIL HEARING.

04:42.323 --> 04:43.494
IT'S ENTRAPMENT.

04:43.494 --> 04:45.496
SHE FAKED A KIDNAPPING
AND WIRED HERSELF.

04:45.496 --> 04:48.288
SO YOU'RE NOT DISPUTING
MR. GRAYSON'S ASSERTIONS?

04:48.288 --> 04:50.541
I DON'T HAVE TO
BECAUSE THEY'RE INADMISSIBLE.

04:50.541 --> 04:52.673
IF I MAY, YOUR HONOR.

04:52.673 --> 04:55.836
[ SPECTATORS MURMUR ]
 YOU DOUBTLESS RECOGNIZE
THE RUSE THAT COMPELLED ME

04:55.836 --> 05:00.971
TO SPEW THOSE OUTRAGEOUS CLAIMS
WAS OF RUBE GOLDBERGIAN DESIGN!

05:00.971 --> 05:03.844
THE WHEELS OF CONSPIRACY
ARE SHAMELESSLY TURNING HERE,

05:03.844 --> 05:05.426
AND WHAT I SAID TO MY DAUGHTER

05:05.426 --> 05:08.769
WAS OBVIOUSLY THE RESULT OF MY
HAVING MEMORIZED THAT FICTION

05:08.769 --> 05:11.602
FOR A PRESS CONFERENCE
I WAS BEING FORCED TO STAGE!

05:11.602 --> 05:14.935
THAT'S A GOOD TALE,
MR. GRAYSON,

05:14.935 --> 05:18.198
BUT THIS THICK PACKET
OF EVIDENCE I JUST RECEIVED

05:18.198 --> 05:19.360
CONTRADICTS THAT.

05:19.360 --> 05:20.701
[ FOLDER THUDS ]

05:20.701 --> 05:23.283
SO, IF YOU'RE
DONE GRANDSTANDING...

05:23.283 --> 05:25.906
BAIL IS HEREBY DENIED.

05:25.906 --> 05:28.118
MR. GRAYSON WILL BE REMANDED
TO CUSTODY.

05:28.118 --> 05:28.949
[ GAVEL BANGS ]

05:28.949 --> 05:29.910
[ CAMERA SHUTTERS CLICKING ]

05:29.910 --> 05:32.042
[ SPECTATORS MURMURING ]

05:32.042 --> 05:33.163
[ HANDCUFFS CLICK ]

05:33.163 --> 05:34.795
OH, UH,
THERE'S ONE LAST THING,

05:34.795 --> 05:37.217
AND I THINK YOU
OUGHT TO HEAR IT.

05:37.217 --> 05:39.219
IN LIGHT
OF THIS NEW EVIDENCE,

05:39.219 --> 05:42.172
I'M REOPENING
THE DAVID CLARKE INVESTIGATION.

05:42.172 --> 05:43.674
[ SPECTATORS MURMURING ]

05:43.674 --> 05:45.015
AND I PROMISE YOU

05:45.015 --> 05:48.228
THE WHEELS OF JUSTICE
WILL TURN AS QUICKLY FOR HIM

05:48.228 --> 05:50.230
AS I'LL MAKE SURE
THEY WILL FOR YOU.

05:50.230 --> 05:51.311
[ GAVEL BANGS ]

05:51.311 --> 05:52.643
[ INDISTINCT SHOUTING ]

06:21.672 --> 06:25.636
I WAS BEGINNING TO WONDER
IF I WOULD EVER SEE THOSE WORDS.

06:27.558 --> 06:28.769
HERE'S TO YOU, DAVID.

06:30.180 --> 06:33.974
ALL HAIL
THE CONQUERING HERO.

06:33.974 --> 06:35.015
YOU DID IT, EMILY.

06:35.015 --> 06:36.106
WE ALL DID IT.

06:36.106 --> 06:39.570
[ GLASSES CLINKING ]

06:42.573 --> 06:46.827
SEEING HIS FACE JUST REMINDS ME
OF ALL OF THE PEOPLE

06:46.827 --> 06:48.408
WE HAD TO HURT.

06:48.408 --> 06:50.330
STILL CONCERNED ABOUT
WHAT WE DID TO YOUR SISTER?

06:50.330 --> 06:52.242
YEAH, BUT IF [SIGHS]
VICTORIA HADN'T GOTTEN AWAY,

06:52.242 --> 06:53.874
I COULD'VE TOLD CHARLOTTE
THE TRUTH.

06:53.874 --> 06:55.295
INSTEAD,
SHE PROBABLY THINKS

06:55.295 --> 06:58.128
IT'S THE LUNATIC
WHO'S POSING AS HER FATHER.

06:58.128 --> 07:00.671
AND...
SQUATTING IN HIS CABIN.

07:00.671 --> 07:04.134
TURNS OUT...IT IS
THE ONE YOUR GRANDFATHER BUILT.

07:04.134 --> 07:06.717
TITLE TRANSFERRED
TO YOUR DAD, AND...

07:06.717 --> 07:08.098
THE WORLD FORGOT ABOUT IT.

07:08.098 --> 07:09.970
WELL,
SOMEONE'S LIVING THERE NOW.

07:09.970 --> 07:11.141
WHO HAD HIS RING.

07:11.141 --> 07:12.683
I NEED TO FIND OUT
WHO THIS IMPOSTER IS.

07:12.683 --> 07:14.144
YEAH.
LET'S GO.

07:14.144 --> 07:16.056
NO, YOU GUYS HAVE
DONE ENOUGH.

07:16.056 --> 07:18.108
WITH THE KIDNAPPING
INVESTIGATION STILL ACTIVE,

07:18.108 --> 07:20.110
WE CAN'T ALL LEAVE TOWN
AT ONCE.

07:20.110 --> 07:21.772
I'LL TAKE CARE OF HIM.

07:23.904 --> 07:25.696
NON, C'EST TOUT POUR
 LE MOMENT.

07:25.696 --> 07:28.118
MERCI.

07:28.118 --> 07:29.159
[ BEEP ]

07:29.159 --> 07:30.240
[ INDISTINCT TALKING
IN DISTANCE ]

07:30.240 --> 07:31.622
IT'S DONE?

07:31.622 --> 07:34.164
IT'S JUST A MATTER OF SIGNING
THE CONTRACT, BUT YES.

07:34.164 --> 07:36.166
YOU ARE OFFICIALLY
MY SECOND-IN-COMMAND.

07:36.166 --> 07:37.918
[ BOTH LAUGH ]

07:37.918 --> 07:40.210
I'LL FLY OUT TO MEET THE BOARD
ONCE YOU'RE BACK.
 [ CHUCKLES ]

07:40.210 --> 07:41.922
Gideon: I'LL CERTAINLY SAY
GOOD THINGS ABOUT YOU.

07:43.504 --> 07:45.506
GIDEON?

07:45.506 --> 07:47.297
WHAT ARE YOU DOING HERE?

07:47.297 --> 07:49.550
YOU SEEM OKAY.

07:49.550 --> 07:52.182
CONSIDERING
THE CIRCUMSTANCES.

07:52.182 --> 07:54.895
PARIS IS A CIRCUS, SO...

07:54.895 --> 07:56.146
I THOUGHT I'D COME HERE

07:56.146 --> 07:58.268
AND FLY BACK WITH YOU
FOR THE FUNERAL.

07:58.268 --> 08:00.400
YOU'RE MY BIG SISTER,
AFTER ALL.

08:00.400 --> 08:01.401
AND MY BOSS.

08:01.401 --> 08:03.103
I HOPE YOU UNDERSTAND THAT.

08:03.103 --> 08:05.275
I NEVER WANTED TO RUN
THE COMPANY.

08:05.275 --> 08:07.197
BUT WHO CAN SAY NO TO DAD,
RIGHT?

08:07.197 --> 08:08.529
[ SIGHS ]

08:08.529 --> 08:11.201
AND YOU, DANIEL?
NEXT IN LINE.

08:11.201 --> 08:12.072
YEAH.

08:12.072 --> 08:13.163
[ INHALES DEEPLY ]

08:13.163 --> 08:14.494
A LOT'S CHANGED
SINCE THAT SEMESTER

08:14.494 --> 08:16.206
I SHOWED YOU THE ROPES
AT BOARDING SCHOOL.

08:16.206 --> 08:18.168
I CAN SEE THAT.

08:18.168 --> 08:21.171
WHY DON'T WE GO OUT FOR LUNCH
SO I CAN GET UP TO SPEED?

08:21.171 --> 08:22.623
AND WE'LL JUST...

08:22.623 --> 08:25.085
SAVE THE TEARS FOR PARIS,
OKAY?

08:30.260 --> 08:31.221
[ KNOCK ON DOOR ]

08:36.687 --> 08:38.979
I KNOW I WAS AN IDIOT.

08:38.979 --> 08:42.402
OKAY?
AND YOU TRIED TO WARN ME.

08:42.402 --> 08:44.855
WELL PLAYED, JAVIER.

08:44.855 --> 08:47.908
I WAS WORRIED YOU WERE HERE
FOR AN APOLOGY.

08:47.908 --> 08:49.319
WELL,
YOU DID BITCH-SLAP ME

08:49.319 --> 08:52.492
IN FRONT OF THE PEOPLE
I WAS HOPING TO CALL MY PEERS.

08:52.492 --> 08:54.705
THOUGH, I GUESS,
IN COMPARISON

08:54.705 --> 08:56.496
TO EVERYTHING ELSE
THAT'S HAPPENED,

08:56.496 --> 08:58.038
IT'S SMALL CHANGE,
RIGHT?

08:58.038 --> 09:00.831
HAS BEEN
AN EVENTFUL FEW DAYS.

09:00.831 --> 09:03.163
BEEN OUT OF JAIL
A COUPLE WEEKS.

09:03.163 --> 09:05.716
ALREADY LOST MY JOB,
MY APP...

09:05.716 --> 09:07.427
MY MENTOR...

09:08.218 --> 09:11.882
...AND MY ANKLE MONITOR,
WHICH IS, UH...

09:11.882 --> 09:13.513
WHY I'M GONNA BLOW TOWN
FOR A BIT.

09:13.513 --> 09:15.636
WELL,
DON'T GO TOO FAR.

09:15.636 --> 09:18.098
I'VE GOT BIG PLANS
FOR MYCLONE.

09:18.098 --> 09:19.099
WHAT'S THE POINT?

09:19.099 --> 09:21.812
IT'S NOT EVEN OURS ANYMORE,
MAN.

09:21.812 --> 09:23.233
FOR NOW.

09:23.233 --> 09:26.566
[ SIGHS ]
ALL RIGHT.

09:27.608 --> 09:29.069
[ BUZZER ]

09:31.451 --> 09:33.784
[ SIGHS ] YOU KNOW, I PRIDE
MYSELF ON BEING PREPARED.

09:33.784 --> 09:35.495
HELL, THAT'S
WHAT YOU PAY ME FOR.

09:35.495 --> 09:38.578
WELL, THEN, YOU'D BETTER HAVE
A DAMN GOOD NEXT MOVE.

09:38.578 --> 09:40.751
WHAT'S MORE CONCERNING
IS THEIRS.

09:40.751 --> 09:44.665
THE FEDS REOPENED THE INQUIRY
INTO PASCAL LeMARCHAL'S DEATH,

09:44.665 --> 09:47.918
AND YOU NOW HAVE MOTIVE
BECAUSE THEY HAVE THIS.

09:52.713 --> 09:54.174
[ SLAMS TABLE ]

09:54.174 --> 09:55.676
[ SIGHS ]

09:55.676 --> 09:59.890
YOU'RE LOOKING AT...MURDER,
CONSPIRACY TO SUPPORT TERRORISM,

09:59.890 --> 10:01.061
PERJURY, JURY TAMPERING.

10:01.061 --> 10:02.643
AND THEY'RE
JUST GETTING STARTED.

10:02.643 --> 10:04.104
UH...

10:04.104 --> 10:09.109
MAYBE IT'S TIME
TO CONSIDER TAKING A PLEA.

10:09.109 --> 10:11.071
FOR WHAT?

10:12.152 --> 10:13.363
LIFE IN PRISON.

10:19.289 --> 10:22.412
KURT: So, the tests confirm
what you thought?

10:22.412 --> 10:25.125
ONLY THAT THE LIAR
WHO CALLED HERSELF AMANDA CLARKE

10:25.125 --> 10:27.127
WAS IN NO WAY RELATED
TO DAVID.

10:27.127 --> 10:28.298
If she were,

10:28.298 --> 10:31.211
her son would share DNA
with Charlotte.

10:31.211 --> 10:33.253
[ SIGHS ] ARE YOU GONNA WRITE
ANOTHER LETTER FOR ME TO SEND?

10:33.253 --> 10:36.136
No.
Just be ready to finish the job.

10:36.136 --> 10:39.179
What makes you think
Emily is gonna follow the lead?

10:39.179 --> 10:42.312
BECAUSE WHAT ELSE
WOULD A DOTING DAUGHTER DO?

10:45.065 --> 10:47.067
[ BIRDS CHIRPING,
LEAVES RUSTLING ]

10:53.273 --> 10:55.275
[ DOOR HINGES CREAK ]

11:13.053 --> 11:13.924
[ CREAK ]

11:32.733 --> 11:33.984
[ BREATHING HEAVILY ]

11:34.815 --> 11:36.486
UNH!

11:46.416 --> 11:49.750
[ BREATHING HEAVILY ]

12:02.722 --> 12:04.895
I SHOULD'VE GONE
WITH YOU.

12:04.895 --> 12:06.686
I'M FINE. HE'S NOT.

12:08.188 --> 12:10.981
AND WHAT IF THERE HAD BEEN
MORE THAN ONE OF THEM?

12:10.981 --> 12:13.443
WE HAVE GONE TOO FAR
TO TAKE A MISSTEP NOW.

12:14.614 --> 12:16.236
IF I LOST YOU --
 YOU WON'T.

12:16.236 --> 12:18.238
GOOD.

12:18.238 --> 12:19.659
BUT WHO THE HELL WAS HE?

12:19.659 --> 12:21.992
WHOEVER HE WAS,
HE WAS WORKING FOR VICTORIA.

12:21.992 --> 12:24.955
HIS PHONE SHOWED THAT THEY SPOKE
THIS MORNING.

12:24.955 --> 12:28.999
I THINK SHE WANTED HIM
TO GET A DNA SAMPLE FROM ME.

12:28.999 --> 12:30.670
SO SHE'S ON TO YOU.

12:30.670 --> 12:32.172
SHE THINKS
SHE'S IN THE CLEAR,

12:32.172 --> 12:33.333
BUT THERE'S ONE PERSON

12:33.333 --> 12:35.335
WHO CAN LINK HER
TO MY FATHER'S FRAME-UP.

12:36.636 --> 12:38.178
MICHELLE BANKS.

12:38.178 --> 12:39.800
THE THERAPIST
WHO LOCKED YOU AWAY.

12:39.800 --> 12:40.881
AND BRAINWASHED ME

12:40.881 --> 12:42.762
INTO BELIEVING
THAT MY FATHER WAS EVIL.

12:42.762 --> 12:44.224
[ INHALES DEEPLY ]

12:44.224 --> 12:47.307
I GOT RESULTS ONCE
BY POSING AS HER PATIENT.

12:47.307 --> 12:48.518
SO YOU CAN'T GO AGAIN.

12:49.940 --> 12:51.892
THEN I'LL CONVINCE HER
TO COME CLEAN.

12:51.892 --> 12:53.984
GIVEN WHAT'S HAPPENING
WITH YOUR FATHER,

12:53.984 --> 12:55.986
SHE SHOULD BE PREPARED
FOR THE TRUTH TO COME TO LIGHT.

12:55.986 --> 12:59.489
[ SIGHS ]

12:59.489 --> 13:00.901
I CAN'T BELIEVE IT.

13:00.901 --> 13:04.454
PEOPLE ARE FINALLY TALKING
ABOUT MY FATHER'S INNOCENCE.

13:04.454 --> 13:06.616
SOON, EVERYTHING WILL BE
OUT IN THE OPEN.

13:08.959 --> 13:09.960
INCLUDING US.

13:12.002 --> 13:14.004
I CAN'T WAIT TO SEE
WHAT THAT FEELS LIKE.

13:16.126 --> 13:22.092
SO...YOU AND MARGAUX SHARE
A FATHER, A HOMELAND,

13:22.092 --> 13:24.134
BUT...NOT AN ACCENT.

13:24.134 --> 13:25.725
NOR A MOTHER.

13:25.725 --> 13:27.057
AFTER A NASTY DIVORCE,

13:27.057 --> 13:29.389
SHE SENT ME TO BOARDING SCHOOL,
TO NEW HAMPSHIRE,

13:29.389 --> 13:30.560
JUST TO PISS HIM OFF.

13:30.560 --> 13:33.023
INNER-FAMILY FIGHTING
IS JUST A...

13:33.023 --> 13:35.105
LeMARCHAL TRADITION.

13:35.105 --> 13:36.937
Nolan: WELL, THAT EXPLAINS
WHY YOU WERE...

13:36.937 --> 13:39.819
SO RECEPTIVE
WHEN I CALLED YOU.

13:39.819 --> 13:42.702
MY SISTER STOLE THE COMPANY
OUT FROM UNDER ME

13:42.702 --> 13:45.325
AND NOW HAS POSSESSION
OF MYCLONE --

13:45.325 --> 13:47.497
A BILLION-DOLLAR PROPERTY
THAT ONLY YOU CAN FIX.

13:47.497 --> 13:49.789
HAVE FIXED, MY FRIEND.

13:49.789 --> 13:53.503
IT'LL BE MULTIBILLION
BY THE TIME YOU TAKE THE REINS

13:53.503 --> 13:54.955
AND WE PARTNER UP.

13:54.955 --> 13:56.836
YOU MUST REALLY HATE DANIEL
TO TRUST A TOTAL STRANGER.

13:56.836 --> 13:58.758
WELL, YOUR SISTER'S LAPDOG

13:58.758 --> 14:01.631
HAS SET OUT
TO MAKE MY LIFE MISERABLE,

14:01.631 --> 14:05.345
WHICH MAKES YOU
THE BETTER OF TWO EVILS.

14:05.345 --> 14:07.597
WELL, SINCE MARGAUX'S
FIRST ACT OF OFFICE

14:07.597 --> 14:09.599
WAS TO MAKE HIM
SECOND-IN-COMMAND...

14:09.599 --> 14:13.523
WE HURT HIM,
IT HURTS HER, AND THEN...

14:13.523 --> 14:16.856
[CHUCKLES]
 I TAKE OVER.

14:16.856 --> 14:18.528
NOW...

14:18.528 --> 14:20.901
WHAT DO YOU
HAVE IN MIND?

14:23.193 --> 14:24.284
THEY CHECKED THE CABIN

14:24.284 --> 14:25.906
WHERE YOU THINK
YOUR KIDNAPPER LIVED.

14:25.906 --> 14:27.407
THERE WERE
SIGNS OF STRUGGLE.

14:27.407 --> 14:28.658
WE'LL KEEP PURSUING LEADS.

14:28.658 --> 14:30.700
GOD, I'M SORRY
I NEVER HEARD HIS ACTUAL VOICE

14:30.700 --> 14:32.662
OR GOT A GOOD LOOK AT HIM,
DETECTIVE REYES.

14:32.662 --> 14:35.415
DON'T APOLOGIZE, CHARLOTTE.
YOU WERE VERY BRAVE.

14:35.415 --> 14:36.876
AND YOU'RE SAFE NOW.

14:37.877 --> 14:40.000
AM I?

14:40.000 --> 14:41.922
CALL ME IF YOU THINK
OF ANYTHING ELSE.

14:41.922 --> 14:42.882
THANK YOU.

14:46.176 --> 14:50.060
CHARLOTTE, DEAR...
WERE THEY ABLE TO HELP YOU?

14:50.060 --> 14:51.891
DON'T WORRY, MOM.

14:51.891 --> 14:53.974
I DIDN'T TELL THEM ANYTHING
I LEARNED ABOUT YOU.

14:53.974 --> 14:55.895
THAT'S NOT WHAT I --
 SAVE IT.

14:55.895 --> 14:58.478
I'M SURE THIS IS ALREADY
A PRETTY SAD DAY FOR YOU

14:58.478 --> 15:01.821
SINCE MY FATHER'S CASE
HAS BEEN REOPENED...

15:01.821 --> 15:04.444
UNDOING ALL THAT HARD WORK
YOU DID YEARS AGO.

15:04.444 --> 15:06.866
DO NOT CONFUSE CONRAD'S ACTIONS
WITH MINE.

15:06.866 --> 15:09.119
AFTER EVERYTHING
THAT'S TRANSPIRED,

15:09.119 --> 15:11.491
I AM STILL
PUTTING MY CHILDREN FIRST.

15:11.491 --> 15:14.744
I HOPE YOU KNOW
HOW MUCH I LOVE YOU, CHARLOTTE.

15:14.744 --> 15:16.336
OH.

15:16.336 --> 15:18.418
LIKE YOU LOVED DAVID CLARKE?

15:23.503 --> 15:26.506
Man: KEEP MOVING, GENTLEMEN.

15:29.889 --> 15:32.262
STEP OUT OF LINE
IN FRONT OF YOUR CELL.

15:32.262 --> 15:33.763
TURN AND FACE YOUR CELL.

15:33.763 --> 15:35.435
[ INDISTINCT TALKING ]

15:35.435 --> 15:37.978
Mostrowski:
IN YOUR CAGE, RICO.

15:42.232 --> 15:44.024
CLOSE THEM UP ON BLOCK FOUR.

15:44.024 --> 15:45.695
[ BUZZER ]

15:45.695 --> 15:48.948
[ CELL DOORS CLOSING ]
 HOLD OPEN 218.

15:48.948 --> 15:52.072
IS THERE A PROBLEM,
OFFICER...MOSTROWSKI?

15:52.072 --> 15:53.913
NO.

15:53.913 --> 15:54.704
UNH!

15:54.704 --> 15:57.077
YOU SAD PIECE OF CRAP.

15:57.077 --> 16:00.130
NOT SO TOUGH WITHOUT ALL THAT
MONEY TO PROTECT YOU, HUH?

16:00.130 --> 16:02.342
THE ONLY THING I CAN SAY
FOR THE FOLKS ON THE PLANE

16:02.342 --> 16:03.173
IS THEY DIED QUICK.

16:03.173 --> 16:04.674
[ GRUNTS ]

16:04.674 --> 16:06.926
YOU WON'T BE SO LUCKY.

16:06.926 --> 16:09.219
GET OFF ME, RINELLA!

16:09.219 --> 16:11.931
THAT'S ENOUGH, MAN.
COME ON.

16:17.437 --> 16:19.229
Rinella: GET UP.

16:19.229 --> 16:21.311
[ GRUNTS ]

16:21.311 --> 16:23.313
CLOSE 218.

16:23.313 --> 16:24.774
[ BUZZER ]

16:24.774 --> 16:26.446
[ CELL DOOR CLOSES ]

16:31.951 --> 16:34.074
THAT'S FINE.
[ BREATHES DEEPLY ]

16:34.074 --> 16:36.536
I APPRECIATE YOU SEEING ME
ON SUCH SHORT NOTICE.

16:36.536 --> 16:38.418
Michelle: WELL,
I WOULDN'T BE DOING MY JOB

16:38.418 --> 16:39.669
IF I TURNED AWAY SOMEONE

16:39.669 --> 16:42.252
CONCERNED ABOUT THE SAFETY
OF ONE OF MY PATIENTS.

16:42.252 --> 16:44.214
NOW, ON WHOSE BEHALF
ARE YOU HERE?

16:44.214 --> 16:46.216
AN OLD FRIEND OF MINE.

16:46.216 --> 16:48.088
AND YOURS.

16:48.088 --> 16:49.509
AMANDA CLARKE.

16:49.509 --> 16:51.841
MAY SHE REST IN PEACE.

16:51.841 --> 16:53.803
WHO ARE YOU?

16:53.803 --> 16:55.055
OH, THAT'S
NONE OF YOUR CONCERN,

16:55.055 --> 16:56.556
BUT WHAT I IMAGINE HASN'T
ESCAPED YOUR NOTICE

16:56.556 --> 16:57.767
IS THE TRUTH
ABOUT HER FATHER.

16:57.767 --> 16:59.349
[ INHALES DEEPLY ]

16:59.349 --> 17:01.441
CONRAD GRAYSON SHOULD PAY
FOR WHAT HE DID,

17:01.441 --> 17:02.232
DON'T YOU THINK?

17:02.232 --> 17:04.523
WELL, YES.
OF COURSE.

17:04.523 --> 17:05.565
AS SHOULD
EVERYBODY INVOLVED.

17:06.945 --> 17:09.148
I THINK YOU KNOW
WHY I'M HERE.

17:09.148 --> 17:10.910
YOU WANT VICTORIA.

17:13.203 --> 17:14.914
I KNOW
YOU LOCKED AMANDA AWAY

17:14.914 --> 17:16.536
IN EXCHANGE
FOR AN A-LIST CAREER.

17:16.536 --> 17:18.917
SO I WANT THE PROMISE
OF YOUR TESTIMONY,

17:18.917 --> 17:21.961
ANYTHING ELSE YOU HAVE,
AND I WANT IT NOW.

17:26.546 --> 17:28.968
I HAVE RECORDS.
I'LL GO GET THEM.

17:39.349 --> 17:41.941
HE'S ALL YOURS.

17:50.820 --> 17:52.112
[ DOOR OPENS ]

17:53.993 --> 17:55.365
PLEASE FORGIVE MY TARDINESS.

17:55.365 --> 17:58.908
I KNOW HOW SACRED
AFTERNOON TEA IS TO YOU BRITS.

18:00.200 --> 18:01.371
[ INHALES SHARPLY ]

18:02.832 --> 18:04.124
WHAT HAVE YOU DONE?

18:04.124 --> 18:06.206
JUST LEVELED
THE PLAYING FIELD.

18:06.206 --> 18:08.208
I KNEW THAT EMILY
WOULD SEND YOU HERE

18:08.208 --> 18:09.879
TO DO HER DIRTY WORK.
[ SIGHS ]

18:09.879 --> 18:10.970
YOU REALLY DID PICK

18:10.970 --> 18:12.212
THE WRONG GIRL
TO FALL IN LOVE WITH.

18:12.212 --> 18:13.803
GO TO HELL.

18:15.175 --> 18:16.716
[ GRUNTS ]

18:16.716 --> 18:19.679
YOU MUST HATE FEELING
SO VULNERABLE AND MANIPULATED,

18:19.679 --> 18:21.181
MUCH THE WAY
YOU MADE ME FEEL

18:21.181 --> 18:22.642
AFTER YOU MOVED
INTO OUR HOUSE...

18:22.642 --> 18:23.853
AT THE BEGINNING OF SUMMER.

18:23.853 --> 18:25.315
[ BREATHING SHALLOWLY ]

18:25.315 --> 18:27.487
WELL, SUMMER IS FINISHED,
MR. MATHIS.

18:27.487 --> 18:31.781
AND ONCE THAT TOXIN LEADS
TO PARALYSIS...

18:31.781 --> 18:33.233
SO ARE YOU.

18:33.233 --> 18:34.654
[ BREATHING SHALLOWLY ]

18:34.654 --> 18:36.446
[ SHOUTS ]

18:36.446 --> 18:38.037
[ CHOKING ]

18:38.037 --> 18:39.409
[ GRUNTING ]

18:39.409 --> 18:42.202
SQUEEZE THE LIFE OUT OF ME.
[ GASPING ]

18:42.202 --> 18:43.663
DO IT! [ GASPS ]

18:43.663 --> 18:45.375
[ GRUNTING ]

18:49.879 --> 18:51.251
[ GASPS ]

18:51.251 --> 18:54.884
[ GRUNTING, GASPING ]

18:54.884 --> 18:58.017
EMILY RIPPED AWAY MY CHANCE
FOR TRUE LOVE.

18:58.017 --> 19:00.260
[ BREATHING HEAVILY ]

19:00.260 --> 19:02.932
IT'S ONLY FAIR
THAT I DO THE SAME FOR HER.

19:02.932 --> 19:05.265
EMILY WILL WIN.

19:05.265 --> 19:09.269
[ SIGHS ]
 [ CHUCKLES ]

19:09.269 --> 19:11.981
LOYAL TO THE BITTER END.

19:11.981 --> 19:13.943
IT'S A BEAUTIFUL SENTIMENT.

19:17.327 --> 19:20.870
[ BREATHING SHALLOWLY ]

19:20.870 --> 19:23.783
AND AN EVEN BETTER EPITAPH.

19:23.783 --> 19:25.455
[ WHEEZING ]

19:27.667 --> 19:29.289
GOODBYE, MR. MATHIS.

19:32.422 --> 19:35.345
[ GRUNTS, GASPS ]

19:39.138 --> 19:41.431
[ GRUNTING ]

19:48.858 --> 19:49.769
[ GROANS ]

20:03.703 --> 20:05.705
NOLAN, WHAT IS IT?

20:10.380 --> 20:13.793
[ BREATHING HEAVILY ]

20:13.793 --> 20:15.295
JACK...

20:15.295 --> 20:16.215
TURN ON THE TV.

20:18.338 --> 20:20.049
[ TV CLICKS ]

20:20.049 --> 20:23.263
Man:
 THE INFAMOUS CASE OF THE
 UNITED STATES vs. DAVID CLARKE

20:23.263 --> 20:25.435
HAS BEEN REOPENED
 BY THE FBI

20:25.435 --> 20:27.267
DUE TO THE SURFACING
 OF NEW EVIDENCE

20:27.267 --> 20:30.770
BROUGHT TO LIGHT
IN THE TRIAL OF CONRAD GRAYSON.

20:30.770 --> 20:32.191
THE 20-YEAR-OLD CONVICTION

20:32.191 --> 20:34.564
THAT LANDED CLARKE
 IN PRISON FOR LIFE

20:34.564 --> 20:36.406
HAS NOW BEEN
 OFFICIALLY OVERTURNED

20:36.406 --> 20:39.739
BY THE U.S. DISTRICT COURT,
 THUS POSTHUMOUSLY

20:39.739 --> 20:41.781
CLEARING DAVID CLARKE
 OF ALL CRIMES.

20:41.781 --> 20:43.783
AGAIN,
 THAT IS BREAKING NEWS,

20:43.783 --> 20:45.535
AND WE WILL HAVE
 MORE INFORMATION

20:45.535 --> 20:47.287
AS THE NIGHT CONTINUES.
 [ LAUGHS ]

20:50.750 --> 20:52.962
EMILY...
 [ SIGHS ]

20:52.962 --> 20:54.584
...YOU DID THE IMPOSSIBLE.

20:54.584 --> 20:56.756
[ Chuckling ] AND JUST
TWO WEEKS SHY OF YOUR DEADLINE.

20:56.756 --> 20:58.047
[ BOTH LAUGH ]

20:58.047 --> 21:00.139
[ Sighing ]
OH, MY GOD.

21:00.139 --> 21:02.842
[ CHUCKLES SOFTLY ]

21:02.842 --> 21:05.725
I KNOW THAT ALL OF THIS
CAME WITH A PRICE.

21:05.725 --> 21:08.518
STOP.

21:08.518 --> 21:11.481
YOU HAVEN'T ONLY HONORED
YOUR FATHER TODAY.

21:11.481 --> 21:14.193
YOU HONORED DECLAN
AND AMANDA, TOO.

21:14.193 --> 21:16.946
THEY'D BE PROUD OF YOU.

21:18.818 --> 21:21.611
I AM.

21:21.611 --> 21:23.863
[ BOTH CHUCKLE ]

21:23.863 --> 21:26.245
[ SIGHS ]

21:26.245 --> 21:29.369
NO MORE TEARS, OKAY?

21:29.369 --> 21:30.870
THIS IS CAUSE
FOR CELEBRATION.

21:30.870 --> 21:31.871
[ CLEARS THROAT ]

21:31.871 --> 21:34.213
EVERYONE, LISTEN UP.

21:34.213 --> 21:35.755
DRINKS ARE ON THE HOUSE.

21:35.755 --> 21:37.417
[ LAUGHS ]

21:37.417 --> 21:40.470
[ CHEERS AND APPLAUSE ]

21:51.561 --> 21:53.483
HEY.

21:53.483 --> 21:56.235
DID YOU HEAR THE NEWS?

21:56.235 --> 21:59.529
IT HAPPENED.
THEY CLEARED HIM.

22:04.113 --> 22:06.205
AIDEN?

22:06.205 --> 22:08.748
YOU OKAY?

22:12.952 --> 22:13.873
AIDEN?

22:19.669 --> 22:21.010
AIDEN, ARE YOU OKAY?

22:26.305 --> 22:28.728
AIDEN, WAKE UP.

22:28.728 --> 22:29.308
[ GASPS ]

22:29.308 --> 22:32.271
AIDEN, WAKE UP!

22:32.271 --> 22:34.934
NO, NO, NO,
NO, NO.

22:34.934 --> 22:38.187
[ SNIFFLES ]
AIDEN, WAKE UP!!

22:40.440 --> 22:44.444
[ Crying ]
NO! NO, NO!

22:44.444 --> 22:47.577
NO!
[ SOBS ]

22:51.751 --> 22:53.332
[ Crying ] NO!

22:53.332 --> 22:56.205
NO!

22:56.205 --> 22:59.378
NO!

23:05.054 --> 23:06.636
[ DOOR OPENS ]

23:06.636 --> 23:10.430
[ FOOTSTEPS APPROACHING ]

23:10.430 --> 23:11.851
Nolan: EMS?

23:11.851 --> 23:15.975
[ SIGHS ]

23:15.975 --> 23:18.227
[ SIGHS ]

23:18.227 --> 23:21.280
I LOVED HIM.

23:21.280 --> 23:22.692
[ SIGHS ]

23:22.692 --> 23:25.865
MORE THAN I EVER LOVED
ANYBODY.

23:25.865 --> 23:27.366
I KNOW.

23:29.789 --> 23:32.201
WE COULD'VE HAD
A LIFE TOGETHER.

23:35.705 --> 23:37.917
I SHOULD'VE GIVEN EVERYTHING UP,
BUT I COULDN'T.

23:37.917 --> 23:41.711
I-I COULDN'T.

23:46.546 --> 23:49.218
AIDEN...

23:49.218 --> 23:55.184
DEDICATED HIMSELF TO YOUR CAUSE
BECAUSE HE LOVED YOU.

23:55.184 --> 23:57.186
AND NOT EVEN YOU
COULD'VE STOPPED HIM.

23:57.186 --> 23:59.188
I PULLED HIM BACK,
NOLAN.

23:59.188 --> 24:02.401
[ SNIFFLES ]
HE WAS GONE.

24:02.401 --> 24:06.235
AND HE WAS HAPPY.

24:06.235 --> 24:09.529
THIS IS MY FAULT.

24:09.529 --> 24:11.911
YOU KNOW...

24:11.911 --> 24:14.243
AIDEN ONCE TOLD ME
THAT, UH...

24:14.243 --> 24:15.334
[ SNIFFLES ]

24:15.334 --> 24:18.538
...FOR MOST OF HIS LIFE...

24:18.538 --> 24:22.752
HE FELT BROKEN,
BUT...

24:22.752 --> 24:25.214
THAT ALL CHANGED
WHEN HE MET YOU.

24:25.214 --> 24:27.797
[ CRYING ]

24:27.797 --> 24:32.221
YOU...WERE THE REASON
FOR HIM TO LIVE, EMS.

24:35.855 --> 24:38.307
[ SNIFFLES, SIGHS ]

24:38.307 --> 24:42.271
[ SNIFFLES ]
NOW I'VE LOST MINE.

24:48.317 --> 24:53.322
[ SIGHS ]
I JUST DON'T UNDERSTAND.

24:53.322 --> 24:54.534
WHY WOULD EMILY LET
THE AUTHORITIES BELIEVE

24:54.534 --> 24:58.958
THAT AIDEN'S DEATH
WAS A SUICIDE?

24:58.958 --> 25:02.121
THERE'S ONLY ONE REASON.

25:02.121 --> 25:06.255
EMILY KNOWS
THIS WAS VICTORIA.

25:06.255 --> 25:08.888
SHE WANTS HER
ALL TO HERSELF.

25:10.800 --> 25:12.592
YOU DON'T THINK
THAT SHE MIGHT...

25:14.183 --> 25:16.345
NOLAN,
WE CAN'T LET HER.

25:16.345 --> 25:18.137
WHY NOT?

25:18.137 --> 25:19.599
[ SIGHS ]

25:19.599 --> 25:23.312
AIDEN WAS MY FRIEND, TOO.

25:23.312 --> 25:26.816
AND I LOVED HIM.
[ SIGHS ]

25:26.816 --> 25:28.738
VICTORIA DESERVES TO DIE.

25:28.738 --> 25:30.409
I KNOW THAT.

25:30.409 --> 25:32.531
BUT EMILY WAS THIS CLOSE
TO GETTING HER LIFE BACK.

25:32.531 --> 25:34.824
DOING SOMETHING LIKE THAT
MIGHT RIP IT ALL AWAY AGAIN.

25:36.205 --> 25:39.208
SHE NEEDS US.

25:41.540 --> 25:44.333
YOU'RE RIGHT.

25:44.333 --> 25:48.968
WE NEED TO PROTECT HER
BEFORE SHE GOES TOO FAR.

25:58.517 --> 26:01.140
EMILY.
WHAT ARE YOU DOING HERE?

26:01.140 --> 26:05.024
YOU'RE AN ACCOMPLICE
TO MURDER.

26:05.024 --> 26:06.485
SOMETHING HAS TO BE DONE
ABOUT THAT.

26:06.485 --> 26:08.317
I DON'T KNOW
WHAT YOU'RE TALKING ABOUT.

26:08.317 --> 26:09.188
[ LOCK CLICKS ]

26:09.188 --> 26:12.151
DO NOT DENY IT.

26:12.151 --> 26:15.364
I KNOW THAT YOU HELPED VICTORIA
KILL AIDEN MATHIS.

26:15.364 --> 26:18.327
NO, T-THAT'S PREPOSTEROUS.
Y-YOU DON'T HAVE ANY PROOF.

26:18.327 --> 26:19.328
I DON'T NEED PROOF!

26:19.328 --> 26:20.700
I'M NOT GOING
TO THE AUTHORITIES.

26:20.700 --> 26:22.541
I CAN PUNISH YOU
WORSE THAN THEY CAN.

26:22.541 --> 26:25.965
I-I SWEAR, I-I DIDN'T HAVE
ANY IDEA WHAT SHE HAD PLANNED.

26:25.965 --> 26:28.417
I JUST DID
WHAT VICTORIA TOLD ME TO DO.

26:28.417 --> 26:31.210
[ SCOFFS ]
LIKE YOU ALWAYS DID.

26:31.210 --> 26:33.633
[ GASPS ]

26:33.633 --> 26:36.475
LET ME SEE MY DAD.
 NO.

26:36.475 --> 26:39.428
BECAUSE YOU'D ONLY BE
 PRETENDING TO BE GOOD.

26:39.428 --> 26:42.982
LIKE YOUR DAD PRETENDED
 TO BE A GOOD FATHER.

26:42.982 --> 26:46.435
BUT HE WAS
 A GOOD FATHER.

26:46.435 --> 26:48.437
YOU KNOW THE TRUTH.

26:48.437 --> 26:51.490
WHAT DID HE DO?

26:51.490 --> 26:54.363
HE HURT PEOPLE.

26:54.363 --> 26:57.076
Michelle: GO ON.

26:57.076 --> 26:59.829
H-HE KILLED PEOPLE.

27:03.082 --> 27:04.453
AND HE LIED.

27:04.453 --> 27:07.506
GOOD GIRL.

27:07.506 --> 27:09.959
YOU WOULD BE WISE
 TO REMEMBER THAT.

27:09.959 --> 27:11.630
NO.
 NO, NO, NO.

27:11.630 --> 27:12.962
NO!

27:12.962 --> 27:15.755
PLEASE DON'T LEAVE ME IN HERE!
 PLEASE!

27:15.755 --> 27:16.676
[ GASPS ]
 [ KEYBOARD CLACKS ]

27:20.219 --> 27:24.143
THEY DESTROYED DAVID.

27:24.143 --> 27:28.317
AND YOU...
DESTROYED HIS DAUGHTER.

27:32.982 --> 27:35.985
[ GASPS ]
I'M SORRY.

27:37.076 --> 27:39.618
SORRY'S NOT ENOUGH.

27:42.621 --> 27:47.747
"WHEN DESIRE HAS CONCEIVED,
IT GIVES BIRTH TO SIN.

27:47.747 --> 27:52.792
"AND SIN...
WHEN IT IS FULLY GROWN...

27:52.792 --> 27:54.794
GIVES BIRTH TO DEATH."

27:59.678 --> 28:01.801
[ SIGHS ]

28:01.801 --> 28:05.604
AS YOU KNOW,
I WANTED EVERYTHING...

28:05.604 --> 28:10.689
AND ENDED UP WITH NOTHING.

28:10.689 --> 28:14.313
DEATH WOULD BE A LUXURY
COMPARED TO THIS.

28:17.316 --> 28:19.989
[ Weakly ] MY GOD...

28:19.989 --> 28:24.493
WHY ARE MY WANTS
SO FATHOMLESS?

28:24.493 --> 28:27.286
WE ALL HAVE WANTS,
GRAYSON.

28:27.286 --> 28:30.089
THEY JUST COME
WITH A PRICE.

28:31.130 --> 28:33.172
[ SIGHS ]

28:47.847 --> 28:50.399
I'M SURE I'M THE LAST PERSON
YOU WANT TO SEE RIGHT NOW.

28:50.399 --> 28:51.520
GOT THAT RIGHT.

28:53.402 --> 28:57.196
DESPITE ALL OF THE BAD BLOOD
BETWEEN US...

28:57.196 --> 28:59.448
I WANT YOU TO KNOW
THAT I'M HERE FOR YOU.

28:59.448 --> 29:01.450
WHY CAN'T YOU
JUST LEAVE ME ALONE?

29:04.573 --> 29:07.366
BECAUSE JACK FOUND THIS
AT THE CABIN.

29:07.366 --> 29:11.871
Emily: I'M PRETTY SURE
IT BELONGED TO YOUR FATHER.

29:14.633 --> 29:16.045
YOUR ABDUCTOR HAD THAT RING,

29:16.045 --> 29:19.338
WHICH MEANS HE MAY HAVE
DESECRATED DAVID'S GRAVE.

29:19.338 --> 29:22.511
I THINK YOU NEED
TO MOVE HIS BODY TO BE SAFE.

29:23.472 --> 29:27.186
AMANDA WAS MY BEST FRIEND.

29:27.186 --> 29:28.647
SHE WOULD'VE WANTED YOU
TO DO THIS.

29:28.647 --> 29:30.649
HOW DARE YOU SPEAK
FOR AMANDA?

29:30.649 --> 29:33.482
MY FATHER'S NAME
HAS BEEN CLEARED,

29:33.482 --> 29:36.946
AND YOU WANT TO DISTURB
HIS FINAL RESTING PLACE?

29:36.946 --> 29:38.357
GET THE HELL OUT!

29:38.357 --> 29:41.200
FINE.

29:41.200 --> 29:43.362
THEN I'LL DO IT MYSELF.

29:49.788 --> 29:50.910
[ MID-TEMPO RAP MUSIC PLAYS ]

29:50.910 --> 29:51.871
Daniel: OH!

29:51.871 --> 29:53.672
[ LAUGHS ]
ABSINTHE?

29:53.672 --> 29:55.334
REALLY, GID?
 Gideon: YEAH.

29:55.334 --> 29:56.625
YOU KNOW,
THE LAST TIME I DRANK THIS,

29:56.625 --> 29:59.218
I BLACKED OUT AND WOKE UP
IN THE DEAN'S OFFICE.

29:59.218 --> 30:00.970
YOU'RE TRYING TO GET ME
INTO TROUBLE.

30:00.970 --> 30:02.761
THAT'S WHAT YOU'RE
TRYING TO DO.

30:02.761 --> 30:06.185
TELL ME,
HOW'S LIFE IN ACQUISITIONS?

30:06.185 --> 30:08.187
AH, FINE.
I'M JUST...

30:08.187 --> 30:10.639
FAR MORE INTERESTED
IN ACQUIRING SOMETHING ELSE

30:10.639 --> 30:11.640
AT THE MOMENT.

30:11.640 --> 30:14.273
[ RAP MUSIC CONTINUES ]

30:17.396 --> 30:19.278
LET'S INVITE THEM OVER.

30:19.278 --> 30:22.571
I CAN CRY ABOUT MY DAD,
AND YOU CAN CRY ABOUT YOURS.

30:22.571 --> 30:25.284
AND THEY'LL BE PUTTY
IN OUR HANDS.

30:25.284 --> 30:26.946
I'LL EVEN LET YOU
TAKE THE REDHEAD.

30:28.367 --> 30:30.249
[ LAUGHS ]
YOU --

30:30.249 --> 30:31.370
[ BREATHES DEEPLY ]

30:31.370 --> 30:32.751
I MAY NOT HAVE SEEN YOU
IN 10 YEARS,

30:32.751 --> 30:35.584
BUT I KNOW HOW YOU OPERATE.

30:35.584 --> 30:36.956
WHY ARE YOU REALLY HERE,
GID?

30:39.718 --> 30:42.511
I'M PLANNING
TO START MY OWN FIRM.

30:42.511 --> 30:43.842
I'M BUTTERING MARGAUX UP

30:43.842 --> 30:45.965
SO SHE WON'T BE SO PISSED
WHEN I RESIGN.

30:45.965 --> 30:48.347
WELL,
IN THAT CASE, I'M --

30:48.347 --> 30:50.519
I'M GLAD EVERYTHING'S
OUT IN THE OPEN.

30:50.519 --> 30:53.602
I'LL DRINK TO THAT.

30:53.602 --> 30:55.774
[ GLASSES CLINK ]

31:02.401 --> 31:03.362
Victoria:
STOP!

31:03.362 --> 31:05.244
I NEED TO GET OUT
OF THIS HOUSE!

31:05.244 --> 31:07.326
YOU'RE NOT GOING
TO SEE EMILY THORNE!

31:07.326 --> 31:08.617
I HEARD ABOUT HER VISIT.

31:08.617 --> 31:09.868
IF YOU MUST KNOW,

31:09.868 --> 31:11.951
I DESPISE HER ALMOST AS MUCH
AS I DESPISE YOU.

31:11.951 --> 31:15.204
OH, I ASSURE YOU THAT SHE WILL
FAR SURPASS ME ON THAT LIST

31:15.204 --> 31:16.665
ONCE CERTAIN TRUTHS
COME TO LIGHT.

31:16.665 --> 31:17.917
[ SIGHS ]

31:17.917 --> 31:21.961
GOD, MOM, YOU SOUND
JUST AS CRAZY AS SHE DID.

31:21.961 --> 31:25.094
[ DOOR SLAMS ]
 WHAT DID SHE SAY, EXACTLY?

31:25.094 --> 31:27.636
[ SHOVEL SCRAPES ]

31:40.519 --> 31:42.861
I KNOW YOU'RE THERE.

31:48.697 --> 31:50.739
FROM THE SECOND
I LAID EYES ON YOU,

31:50.739 --> 31:52.411
I KNEW SOMETHING WAS WRONG.

31:52.411 --> 31:55.664
AND NOW THIS IS
WHERE IT ALL ENDS.

31:55.664 --> 31:57.166
FITTING.

31:59.378 --> 32:01.840
I DON'T THINK WE'VE COME
TO THE END JUST YET, VICTORIA.

32:01.840 --> 32:04.173
WELL, I'M CERTAIN
THE AUTHORITIES WILL DISAGREE

32:04.173 --> 32:05.004
ONCE THEY ARRIVE.

32:05.004 --> 32:07.306
LET THEM COME.

32:07.306 --> 32:09.428
YOU'RE THE MURDERER HERE.

32:12.761 --> 32:14.974
YOU RECEIVED MY GIFT.

32:14.974 --> 32:17.816
AFTER WHAT YOU'VE DONE
TO THE ONES I LOVE,

32:17.816 --> 32:19.728
YOU DESERVE FAR WORSE!

32:19.728 --> 32:20.939
[ SHOVEL CLATTERS ]

32:20.939 --> 32:23.482
I SHOULD KILL YOU
RIGHT NOW.

32:23.482 --> 32:24.733
I'D GET AWAY WITH IT.

32:24.733 --> 32:26.945
NO ONE WOULD MISS YOU.

32:26.945 --> 32:28.527
NO ONE WOULD MOURN YOU.

32:28.527 --> 32:30.779
YOU DESTROY EVERYONE
WHO GETS CLOSE.

32:30.779 --> 32:32.701
LIKE YOUR FATHER?

32:37.076 --> 32:38.537
ALL RIGHT, LET'S PLAY.

32:40.289 --> 32:42.631
AMANDA CLARKE CHANGES
HER IDENTITY

32:42.631 --> 32:44.963
AND MOVES
INTO THE HOUSE NEXT DOOR

32:44.963 --> 32:46.085
TO SEEK REVENGE.

32:48.427 --> 32:49.588
WELL, THE TRUTH IS

32:49.588 --> 32:51.510
THAT THE MAN THAT YOU REMEMBER
AS YOUR FATHER

32:51.510 --> 32:55.304
AND THE MAN I KNEW...
WERE VERY DIFFERENT.

32:55.304 --> 32:57.266
JUST BECAUSE
YOU THINK YOU KNOW SOMETHING,

32:57.266 --> 32:58.437
IT DOESN'T MAKE IT TRUE.

32:58.437 --> 33:00.649
THEN WHY ARE YOU HERE
DIGGING UP HIS GRAVE?

33:00.649 --> 33:03.312
THAT'S WHERE YOU'RE WRONG.

33:03.312 --> 33:06.315
I'M NOT DIGGING UP
MY FATHER'S GRAVE.

33:13.322 --> 33:15.534
AMANDA.

33:16.325 --> 33:17.666
BUT WHY?

33:28.797 --> 33:30.129
NOLAN:
Did you find her?

33:30.129 --> 33:31.550
NO. I'VE LOOKED
EVERYWHERE I CAN THINK OF.

33:31.550 --> 33:32.841
ANY LUCK TRACKING HER PHONE?

33:32.841 --> 33:34.633
I just found it...

33:34.633 --> 33:35.934
IN THE TOILET.

33:35.934 --> 33:38.847
SHE DITCHED IT IN THE TANK
SO I COULDN'T TRACK HER.

33:38.847 --> 33:40.519
LOOK, I'M JUST --
[ SIGHS ]

33:40.519 --> 33:42.311
I'M GONNA STAY
AT THE BEACH HOUSE

33:42.311 --> 33:43.442
UNTIL SHE TURNS UP.

33:43.442 --> 33:45.234
WHAT THE HELL IS SHE DOING,
JACK?

33:45.234 --> 33:46.565
I DON'T KNOW.

33:46.565 --> 33:48.737
LET'S JUST HOPE IT ISN'T
SOMETHING SHE'LL REGRET.

33:48.737 --> 33:49.738
[ INDISTINCT TALKING ]

33:49.738 --> 33:52.241
I GOT TO GO.
KEEP ME POSTED.

33:52.241 --> 33:54.153
WHY DID YOU HIDE THIS
FROM ME?!

33:54.153 --> 33:57.286
I DIDN'T WANT YOU TO GET
YOUR HOPES UP UNNECESSARILY.

33:57.286 --> 34:00.249
I WANTED TO MAKE SURE
IT WAS REALLY DAVID'S FIRST.

34:00.249 --> 34:01.620
SO YOU WENT TO EMILY?

34:01.620 --> 34:04.373
[ SIGHS ]
 SHE HAS NOTHING TO DO
WITH THIS.

34:04.373 --> 34:05.424
HE'S MY FATHER.

34:05.424 --> 34:07.586
WHAT ARE YOU HIDING
FROM ME, JACK?

34:07.586 --> 34:10.429
TELL ME ONCE AND FOR ALL.

34:13.762 --> 34:14.933
THAT'S WHAT I THOUGHT.

34:14.933 --> 34:17.846
CHARLOTTE, PLEASE WAIT.

34:17.846 --> 34:19.558
[ HANDCUFFS CLICK ]

34:21.270 --> 34:22.811
[ CRYING ]

34:32.491 --> 34:34.902
[ GASPS ]

34:34.902 --> 34:36.905
I HAVE TO GO.

34:57.806 --> 34:59.718
Mostrowski:
THANKS FOR COMING, FATHER.

34:59.718 --> 35:01.310
VISITOR EXIT --
GATE "A."

35:01.310 --> 35:03.222
[ BUZZER ]

35:07.896 --> 35:09.107
[ SIGHS ]

35:09.107 --> 35:11.900
AND TO THINK
I WAS EXPECTING ANOTHER BEATING.

35:11.900 --> 35:12.861
[ CHUCKLES ]

35:12.861 --> 35:14.363
PEOPLE THINK I HATE YOU,

35:14.363 --> 35:16.785
NO ONE LOOKS AT ME
WHEN YOU'RE GONE.

35:16.785 --> 35:21.290
TRANSPORTATION WILL MEET YOU
ABOUT A MILE SOUTH.

35:21.290 --> 35:24.082
BLESS YOU, MY SON.

35:24.082 --> 35:27.746
THE RICHES OF HEAVEN
SURELY AWAIT YOU...

35:27.746 --> 35:30.839
[Chuckling]
IN YOUR CHECKING ACCOUNT.

35:30.839 --> 35:32.381
CLOSE THEM UP --
GATE "A."

35:32.381 --> 35:33.422
[ BUZZER ]

35:39.718 --> 35:41.810
[ CELLPHONE VIBRATING ]

35:49.478 --> 35:51.820
[ SIGHS ]

35:51.820 --> 35:52.941
HELLO?

35:52.941 --> 35:54.323
MARGAUX:
Hey, it's me.

35:54.323 --> 35:55.824
Sorry to call so late.

35:55.824 --> 35:57.536
HOW DID IT GO WITH GIDEON?

35:57.536 --> 35:59.828
Oh, we have nothing
to worry about.

35:59.828 --> 36:01.740
He's gonna try
to start his own company,

36:01.740 --> 36:02.951
which will be a joke.

36:02.951 --> 36:04.413
OH, THAT'S A RELIEF.

36:04.413 --> 36:05.704
Where are you now?

36:05.704 --> 36:08.166
[ SIGHS ]
I THINK I HAD A FEW TOO MANY.

36:08.166 --> 36:09.748
GIDEON MUST'VE...

36:09.748 --> 36:12.791
BOOKED ME INTO A ROOM
TO SLEEP IT OFF.

36:12.791 --> 36:14.673
Hey,
now that we're both up,

36:14.673 --> 36:17.886
I hate to let a suite
at the Sassen go to waste.

36:17.886 --> 36:20.138
Maybe join me
for a nightcap?

36:20.138 --> 36:22.561
I'M ON MY WAY.
 Perfect.

36:28.807 --> 36:30.188
Nolan: WAIT.

36:30.188 --> 36:31.520
[ SCOFFS ]

36:31.520 --> 36:33.522
IS SHE --

36:33.522 --> 36:34.523
DID YOU --

36:34.523 --> 36:35.654
I DIDN'T DO IT.

36:35.654 --> 36:37.906
I PAID HER IN COKE,
PER HER REQUEST.

36:37.906 --> 36:40.279
SHE'S THE ONE
WHO DIDN'T KNOW HER OWN LIMITS.

36:40.279 --> 36:41.990
YOU DIDN'T TRY
TO SAVE HER?

36:41.990 --> 36:43.492
AND INCRIMINATE MYSELF?

36:43.492 --> 36:45.284
THERE WAS NOTHING I COULD DO.

36:45.284 --> 36:49.127
BESIDES, NOW WE HAVE THE PHOTO
WE'LL USE TO BLACKMAIL DANNY.

36:49.127 --> 36:51.129
[ CHUCKLES ]
IT'S A WIN-WIN.

36:51.129 --> 36:53.292
THIS ISN'T
HOW I DO BUSINESS.

36:53.292 --> 36:54.423
WELL, IT IS NOW.

36:55.544 --> 36:57.636
I'LL BE IN TOUCH.

37:06.184 --> 37:08.106
WHERE ARE YOU, EMILY?

37:08.106 --> 37:11.610
[ MID-TEMPO MUSIC PLAYS
IN DISTANCE ]

37:11.610 --> 37:13.732
JACK PORTER?

37:13.732 --> 37:15.774
IS EVERYTHING OKAY?

37:15.774 --> 37:17.115
I'M AFRAID NOT.

37:17.115 --> 37:18.737
WE HAVE REASON TO BELIEVE
THAT YOU HAVE INFORMATION

37:18.737 --> 37:20.529
ABOUT THE ABDUCTION
OF CHARLOTTE CLARKE.

37:20.529 --> 37:21.950
WE'RE GONNA NEED YOU
TO COME DOWN TO THE STATION

37:21.950 --> 37:23.412
FOR SOME QUESTIONING.

37:23.412 --> 37:24.783
I WISH I COULD HELP YOU,
BUT --

37:24.783 --> 37:26.415
WE CAN DO THIS
THE EASY WAY...

37:26.415 --> 37:28.457
[ HANDCUFFS RATTLE ]
 ...OR THE HARD WAY...

37:28.457 --> 37:29.748
MR. PORTER.

37:29.748 --> 37:31.710
FOLLOW ME.

37:46.475 --> 37:49.187
Conrad:
♪ SOFTLY ♪

37:49.187 --> 37:54.893
♪ I WILL LEAVE YOU SOFTLY ♪

37:54.893 --> 37:59.608
♪ FOR MY HEART WOULD BREAK ♪

37:59.608 --> 38:02.901
♪ IF YOU SHOULD WAKE ♪

38:02.901 --> 38:06.785
♪ AND SEE ME GO ♪

38:06.785 --> 38:13.412
♪ SO I LEAVE YOU SOFTLY ♪

38:13.412 --> 38:14.873
[ SNIFFS ]

38:14.873 --> 38:17.466
AH.

38:26.054 --> 38:27.976
NO, IT CAN'T BE.

38:32.020 --> 38:33.392
DAVID?

38:41.940 --> 38:43.822
Conrad:
[ GRUNTING ]

38:50.709 --> 38:52.711
[ FRANK SINATRA'S
"SOFTLY, AS I LEAVE YOU" PLAYS ]

38:52.711 --> 38:56.875
♪ SOFTLY ♪

38:56.875 --> 39:04.342
♪ I WILL LEAVE YOU SOFTLY ♪

39:04.342 --> 39:07.265
♪ AS I LEAVE YOU THERE ♪

39:07.265 --> 39:11.930
[ ENGINE TURNS OVER ]

39:11.930 --> 39:19.938
♪ AS I LEAVE YOU THERE ♪

39:19.938 --> 39:22.941
PASCAL?

39:22.941 --> 39:28.366
[ SIGHS ]

39:28.366 --> 39:29.448
Shh.

39:29.448 --> 39:30.288
[ GASPS ]

39:30.288 --> 39:31.580
DON'T STRUGGLE.

39:31.580 --> 39:33.081
IT'LL ONLY MAKE THINGS WORSE.

39:33.081 --> 39:34.753
WHAT HAVE YOU DONE?

39:34.753 --> 39:36.585
YOU NEEDED HELP.

39:36.585 --> 39:38.837
I HAD NO CHOICE
BUT TO CHECK YOU IN.

39:38.837 --> 39:40.419
CHECK ME IN?

39:40.419 --> 39:41.710
DON'T WORRY.

39:41.710 --> 39:43.712
CLAREMONT PSYCHIATRIC
IS THE BEST.

39:45.804 --> 39:47.766
HELP ME!

39:47.766 --> 39:49.718
SOMEONE HELP ME, PLEASE!

39:49.718 --> 39:51.810
YOU WON'T GET AWAY
WITH THIS!

39:51.810 --> 39:52.721
WATCH ME.

39:53.852 --> 39:55.313
[ DOOR OPENS ]

39:55.313 --> 39:56.775
WHAT SEEMS TO BE
THE PROBLEM?

39:56.775 --> 39:58.727
SHE JUST WOKE UP.
SHE'S PANICKING.

39:58.727 --> 39:59.858
I DON'T BELONG HERE.

39:59.858 --> 40:01.610
YOU'VE BEEN DECEIVED
BY THIS WOMAN!

40:01.610 --> 40:02.941
[ BREATHING HEAVILY ]

40:02.941 --> 40:05.023
SHE'S BEEN RUNNING AROUND
UNDER A FALSE IDENTITY.

40:05.023 --> 40:06.525
SHE'S AMANDA CLARKE!

40:06.525 --> 40:07.826
[ SIGHS ]

40:07.826 --> 40:10.198
SHE'S BEEN OBSESSING
OVER THIS THEORY FOR MONTHS.

40:10.198 --> 40:12.701
WHEN I FOUND HER...
DIGGING UP AMANDA'S GRAVE,

40:12.701 --> 40:15.163
I-I TRIED TO CALM HER DOWN,
BUT SHE ATTACKED ME.

40:15.163 --> 40:16.705
SHE'S LYING!

40:16.705 --> 40:19.628
THE AUTHORITIES INITIATED
A 5150 AND BROUGHT YOU HERE.

40:19.628 --> 40:20.799
YOU CAN'T
LEGALLY HOLD ME HERE

40:20.799 --> 40:22.040
WITHOUT THE AUTHORITY
OF ANOTHER DOCTOR!

40:22.040 --> 40:24.042
OH, BUT WE HAVE ONE.

40:24.042 --> 40:24.803
YOURS.

40:26.344 --> 40:27.506
MICHELLE?

40:27.506 --> 40:28.757
DOCTOR,
THESE ARE MY NOTES

40:28.757 --> 40:30.809
FROM MY SESSIONS
WITH MRS. GRAYSON.

40:30.809 --> 40:32.891
THEY DETAIL HER OBSESSION
WITH MISS THORNE,

40:32.891 --> 40:34.933
SPIRALING
INTO ACUTE PSYCHOSIS.

40:34.933 --> 40:36.014
LIAR!

40:36.014 --> 40:37.766
[ SIGHS ]
I JUST WANT HER TO BE OKAY.

40:37.766 --> 40:38.477
NO!

40:38.477 --> 40:40.058
THANK YOU, DR. JOHNSON.

40:40.058 --> 40:41.109
DR. BANKS.

40:42.150 --> 40:43.612
DON'T YOU DARE.

40:43.612 --> 40:45.323
[ GASPS ]
DON'T YOU DARE!

40:45.323 --> 40:46.404
DON'T YOU DARE!!

40:46.404 --> 40:48.827
GOODBYE, VICTORIA.

40:48.827 --> 40:50.028
[ GROANS ]

40:50.028 --> 40:51.570
GET BETTER SOON.

40:51.570 --> 40:52.741
SHE'S AMANDA CLARKE!

40:52.741 --> 40:54.412
SHE'S AMANDA CLARKE!

40:54.412 --> 40:57.626
SHE'S AMANDA CLARKE!
SHE'S AMANDA CLARKE!!

40:57.626 --> 40:59.538
SHE'S AMANDA CLARKE!

40:59.538 --> 41:00.709
SHE'S AMANDA CLARKE!

41:00.709 --> 41:02.460
SHE'S AMANDA CLARKE!
[ GASPS ]

41:02.460 --> 41:04.212
[ Crying ]
SHE'S AMANDA CLARKE!

41:04.212 --> 41:05.634
SHE'S AMANDA CLARKE!

41:05.634 --> 41:07.716
SHE'S AMANDA CLARKE!
